                <h2 class="subheading">Why Choose an EV Over an ICE Vehicle?</h2>
                <p>Here's why choosing an EV over an ICE (internal combustion engine) vehicle is a smart move—covering cost, performance, environment, convenience, and long-term value:</p>

                <h3 class="subheading">1. Much Lower Operating & Maintenance Costs</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Fuel running cost:</span> In India, EVs typically consume ₹1–2/km, while petrol/diesel cars cost around ₹5–7/km.</li>
